DISCLAIMER:
This software is a prototype/educational project and is not intended for medical
use. It should not be used to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.
For medical advice, please consult with a qualified healthcare professional.

The anomaly detection features are for educational demonstration purposes only
and should not be relied upon for making health-related decisions.

Any production deployment would require:
- Clinical validation studies
- Regulatory approval (FDA, CE marking, etc.)
- HIPAA compliance
- Professional medical oversight
- Proper security audits
- Liability insurance
